{"tid":593451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南生圍縱火案　樂手睹口罩人徘徊 重案組接手調查","createTime":"2018-03-15T04:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T05:08:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdc36045cfadb5e7f338f1a5ec22343969472a8","tid":593451,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:04:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180315/20332144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332144&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=64a563be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332144&h=52661e59\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180315/20332144</a><br />\n<br />\n南生圍縱火案　樂手睹口罩人徘徊<br />\n重案組接手調查<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】南生圍連續兩日發生的火警，令受影響的面積比前日擴大一倍至12公頃，案件暫列縱火，合併由元朗警區重案組接手調查，暫無人被捕。有樂隊本周一發生火警期間在場拍攝MV，目睹數名戴口罩的男子形迹可疑，在附近徘徊監察，昨到警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n記者：劉柏麟　姜偉康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方、消防處及漁護署昨分別派員到南生圍視察，重案組7至8名探員到場調查，並在場拍攝燒毀狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/15la9p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2F15la9p01.jpg&h=93ef5727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重案組探員昨返回南生圍火場搜證及調查。<br />\n劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/15la9p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2F15la9p02.jpg&h=1d6050c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南生圍路一處燒過位置有樹木冒煙，消防到場灌救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/a1001a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2Fa1001a.gif&h=792587e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火警影響範圍擴至12公頃<br />\n<br />\n漁護署昨指受火警影響範圍比前日所見擴大一倍至12公頃，署方會繼續密切監察。警方呼籲，任何人如目擊本周一及二的案發經過或有資料提供，可致電3661 4645與警方聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n樂隊PHOON周一下午5時許到南生圍拍MV時，山火已焚燒中，樂隊主音木子發現3名戴口罩中年漢踩單車，不斷在附近徘徊巡視，口罩漢見他們有攝影器材，上前查探他們是否記者。而在另一位置，MV導演則目睹有一輛紫色平治房車來回穿梭，見有途人駐足觀看山火時，車上兩人即調低車窗，以不友善目光怒視對方，「係咁睥住人，似係想趕人走」。<br />\n<br />\n他們認為現場有數個火頭及在濕度高的環境下起火不尋常，木子說：「你話陰謀論又好，聯想又好，希望提供資料畀警方，等佢哋追查有冇可疑。」他昨午由立法會議員鄺俊宇陪同到警署報案。鄺感激有巿民挺身而出，認為不能再讓兇徒逍遙法外，寄望警方嚴正調查。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區區議員黃偉賢表示，正籌劃商討火災的後續工作，包括植樹運動，但因當中涉及私人土地，要先得到業主同意。黃稍後會聯絡大業主恒基，了解他們有何措施可完善保護南生圍。<br />\n<br />\n南生圍發展有限公司認為是次起火原因有可疑，於前日已報警，昨向警方提供資料，望警方盡早破案。長春社公共事務經理吳希文稱，南生圍內的樹木多屬外來品種，例如桉樹，透過人為植樹，相比重新種植本地品種的時間稍短，但都需以年計。至於蘆葦屬粗生植物，在現時潮濕及踏入初夏的時間容易重新生長。不過，對於長遠生態影響，吳指目前難以估計，需仔細觀察。"},{"pid":"87f0459da04de095af60d608dd9695cd19cf983a","tid":593451,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"咪同一班人黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec17999a16c9c0b3b2728f07d85de2c37e2f844","tid":593451,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55848489001fd988b073f6af9471360cbdbf2119","tid":593451,"uid":96007,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"捉到人又點<br />\n都係頂個罪名<br />\n真正嘅惡人繼續享受住佢嘅財富"},{"pid":"e7f5aee706a128f54ee6f7e2c1420a048d5de971","tid":593451,"uid":48161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"唔願信命甜心早注定"},{"pid":"8699821e0c4b3e99bcade7117aab2f71b11ec892","tid":593451,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba53eb15a48f6f28da45ed39a6a34f91656fd848","tid":593451,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f5aee706a128f54ee6f7e2c1420a048d5de971","tid":593451,"uid":48161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"唔願信命甜心早注定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"玄牛導致唐樓火警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2652c98285f60b7823fc688643448d2ca33a5c","tid":593451,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"放果個坐又點，都收哂安家費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263f5112b63809b2f4eb28fabc4a83124839b5e4","tid":593451,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>點解仔孫仲有屎弗既？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3dfc9fb3339e0437f71a59695a604e95cfa93b9a","tid":593451,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"過兩日無人記得啦"},{"pid":"d84df8b2a5db0ac2d08e69cbdde3175a5aae83eb","tid":593451,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"擺明係數字叔做 吹撚漲"},{"pid":"fd1efa1b6c9e176785d395ac685daa0e0fa6fce3","tid":593451,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d44c048e80ca1732d290a3d3b65f53fe46cf50f","tid":593451,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"四叔做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}